The paper discusses the use of availability codes in cloud storage systems, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC). The analysis of data access time involves information theory (cs.IT) and data structures (cs.DS). The strategies for assigning download requests to servers involve system control (cs.SY) and network infrastructure (cs.NI).
